<h2>What is RTalk?</h2>
<p>RTalk is a truly anonymous chat site. Unlike Facebook or Google, we do not store your chat data or mine your conversations. No ads, no spam, complete privacy. Just you chatting with your friends.</p>

<p>To start a new session, click the New Session button on the home page. A URL will be generated. You can share it as many people as you want to chat with. You may start as many separate sessions as you want.</p>

